Novak Djokovic beat John Isner 7-6 (3), 6-2 in the Miami Open semifinal on Friday night . 
  The No 1-seeded Serbian will face Andy Murray in the final of the Key Biscayne tournament . 
  Murray defeated Tomas Berdych 6-4, 6-3 to reach the final for the third time in his career . 
  The Serbian is aiming to win his fifth title in Miami . 
 